  "text": "As scientific advances have progressed over the last several decades, new distinct headache mechanisms have been uncovered and validated drug targets identified. The barriers to new therapeutic developments are being gradually surmounted. The next several years hold much promise for significant innovations in the management of headache disorders. Parts of this paper were adapted from a previously published article, 1 year ago in this journal written by one of the authors [CITATION_1] .",
